</p><p>The composition of functions is a special case of the <a href="/wiki/Composition_of_relations" title="Composition of relations">composition of relations</a>, sometimes also denoted by <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \circ }">
