"https://archive.org/details/acollectionexam00lacrgoog">[1]</a> (NB. Inhere, Herschel refers to his <a href="#CITEREFHerschel1813">1813 work</a> and mentions <a href="/wiki/Hans_Heinrich_B%C3%BCrmann" title="Hans Heinrich Bürmann">Hans Heinrich Bürmann</a>'s older work.)</span>
